lass=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/en/about\">About<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/en/projects\">Projects<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/en/products\">Products<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/en/quotation\">Quote<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a></nav><div class=\"flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center justify-end gap-2 sm:gap-3\"><div class=\"items-center gap-0.5 rounded-md border border-iba-sky/15 bg-iba-sky/5 p-0.5 hidden sm:inline-flex\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded px-2 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors sm:text-[11px] text-iba-sky/70 hover:bg-white hover:text-iba-sky\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"French\">FR</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded px-2 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors sm:text-[11px] bg-iba-sky text-white\" aria-pressed=\"true\" aria-label=\"English\">EN</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded px-2 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors sm:text-[11px] text-iba-sky/70 hover:bg-white hover:text-iba-sky\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Chinese\">中文</button></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative z-50 inline-flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-iba-sky/5 text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:bg-iba-sky hover:text-white md:hidden\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Open menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button><a class=\"hidden shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-iba-orange px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white transition-colors hover:bg-iba-orange/90 md:inline-flex\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact Us</a></div></div></header><main class=\"flex min-h-[100dvh] md:min-h-screen flex-col bg-background selection:bg-iba-navy selection:text-white\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"VideoObject\",\"name\":\"International Business Alliance - Our mission\",\"description\":\"Provide professionals and individuals with quality materials to ensure the success of their construction projects. We commit to offering tailored solutions, efficient service, and close support for every job site.\",\"uploadDate\":\"2026-07-01T08:00:00+01:00\",\"embedUrl\":\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1204237776?background=1&quality=540p&dnt=1&autopause=0&playsinline=1&api=1\",\"thumbnailUrl\":[\"https://www.afromosia-rdc.com/images/iba-video-thumbnail.jpg\"]}</script><section class=\"relative scroll-mt-20 bg-background pt-[calc(6rem+1.5rem)] pb-16 sm:pt-[calc(7rem+1.5rem)] md:pb-24 overflow-hidden\" aria-labelledby=\"about-page-heading\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center gap-4\"><span class=\"h-px w-12 bg-iba-orange\"></span><p class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">International Business Alliance</p></div><h1 id=\"about-page-heading\" class=\"mt-3 text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.95] tracking-tighter text-iba-sky sm:text-6xl md:text-8xl\">About</h1><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-iba-muted md:text-xl border-l-2 border-iba-orange pl-6\">International Business Alliance — materials, partnerships, and standards serving sustainable construction.</p></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-iba-navy\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-iba-navy py-20 text-white md:py-28 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -right-32 top-0 h-[600px] w-[600px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] blur-[100px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -left-32 bottom-0 h-[400px] w-[400px] rounded-full bg-iba-sky/[0.04] blur-[100px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative mb-10 md:mb-14 lg:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-white/[0.06]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-white/25 bg-white/10 text-white\">Our mission</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70\">01 — Our mission</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white\">Supply, support, and<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-sky italic\">build sustainably.</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-white/80\">Provide professionals and individuals with quality materials to ensure the success of their construction projects. We commit to offering tailored solutions, efficient service, and close support for every job site.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16 lg:items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6 text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/90 md:text-lg\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl border-b border-white/10 pb-4\">A force that builds the future</h3><p class=\"text-xl font-light text-white/95\">We are the force that builds the future — trust that endures over time and across the globe.</p><p class=\"text-white/80\">We do more than supply materials. We support partners and clients in delivering reliable, lasting projects, promoting transparency, safety, and quality.</p></div><aside class=\"group relative lg:col-span-4 overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-iba-sky p-8 shadow-2xl lg:sticky lg:top-32 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 h-1.5 w-full bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-down-right mb-6 h-8 w-8 text-iba-navy opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7 7 10 10\"></path><path d=\"M17 7v10H7\"></path></svg><p class=\"font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">International reach</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/85 md:text-base\">IBA works with foreign and local partners and suppliers, and upholds international standards, enabling it to engage openly with the global construction materials market.</p></div></aside></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180 h-16 md:h-24\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-background\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-x-hidden border-b border-iba-sky/10 bg-background py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-28\" aria-label=\"Vidéo de présentation\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.04]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 2px);background-size:40px 40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto aspect-video w-full min-w-0 overflow-hidden rounded-none border border-iba-sky/15 bg-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_-24px_rgba(40,37,97,0.25)] will-change-transform [transform:translateZ(0)]\" style=\"transform:scale(0.78)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full w-full pointer-events-none [&amp;_iframe]:absolute [&amp;_iframe]:inset-0 [&amp;_iframe]:h-full [&amp;_iframe]:w-full [&amp;_iframe]:border-0\"></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-background py-20 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20 text-center flex flex-col items-center\"><span class=\"mb-6 inline-block font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">Our vision<!-- --> // <!-- -->02 — Our vision</span><h2 class=\"text-balance text-4xl font-black uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter text-iba-sky md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl max-w-5xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">To be a partner of<!-- --> <span class=\"relative inline-block text-iba-navy\">reference in construction.<svg class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3 text-iba-navy/30\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M0,50 L100,50\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"6\"></path></svg></span></h2><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-iba-muted md:text-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">A future where every project, large or small, rests on solid materials and reliable supply. We aspire to become a key industry player by actively contributing to urban development and infrastructure modernization.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-iba-navy\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-x-clip bg-iba-navy py-20 text-white md:py-28 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative mb-10 md:mb-14 lg:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-white/[0.06]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-white/25 bg-white/10 text-white\">Our impact</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70\">03 — Focus areas</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white\">Act with<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-sky\">rigor and measure</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-white/80\">Three complementary levers to ground our mission in concrete results on the ground.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->1</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Targeted impact</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">IBA aims to sustainably improve the construction sector by supplying quality materials, contributing to infrastructure development, and supporting local and regional economic growth.</p></article><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->2</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Our projects</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">A track record of sites and partnerships that demonstrate our ability to deliver, meet standards, and keep our operational commitments.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-flex w-fit items-center border-b border-transparent pb-1 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-all hover:border-white hover:text-white\" href=\"/en/projects\">Explore<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></article><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->3</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Ethical governance</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">IBA practices transparent, responsible management grounded in integrity, respect for standards, legal compliance, and commitment to partners, employees, and clients.</p></article></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180 h-16 md:h-24\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-background\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-background pt-16 pb-24 md:pt-32 lg:pb-40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none flex justify-center opacity-60\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px), \n              linear-gradient(90deg, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:120px 120px;opacity:0.03\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, var(--iba-sky) 2px, transparent 3px);background-size:120px 120px;opacity:0.08\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative lg:mb-16 mb-12 md:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-iba-sky/[0.05]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-iba-sky/15 bg-iba-sky/[0.04] text-iba-sky\">Our charter</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky/55\">04 — Values &amp; principles</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-iba-sky\">Our<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-navy\">philosophy</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-iba-muted\">At IBA, we believe construction sector development rests on responsible management, strong partne